.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: martial-arts, family, documentary, time-travel, sports
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
House: craftsman, wooden, art-deco, cape-cod, cottage
1. the british is the person who likes red
2. the swedish is the art-deco house
3. the danish is the person watching time-travel movies
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the person watching family movies
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the wooden house
7. the person who likes yellow is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the craftsman house
11. the cottages house is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the bluemaster-smoker is the person watching martial-arts movies
13. the german is the prince-smoker
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| House		|     craftsman	|    cottage	|     wooden	|     cape-cod	|      art-deco	|
| Movie-Genre	|    sports	|     time-travel	|     documentary	|    family	|      martial-arts	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
